               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>who resists your attempt to use him as a took, as a means. There is no other point of equally
               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>Now from this follows, in different situation, many different forms of equality.
               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>The democratic form is one form, the liberal form is another—they are sometimes
