               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_3_tl_8" n="N008"/>of OUR concept of equality. And even the Stoic concepts of equality are DETERMINED by their
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_71_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>historial situation much more than by a special abstract formula. There the problem was to give
