               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>situation: neither in early Christianity nor in many periods of American history, Christianity
               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>in the position to Desate SlAVERY AS SUCH. The equality in the idea of Christianity, in Paul,
               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>Philemon—or what was his name?—Onesimus! —
