               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>the discussion in THES country about slavery show one thing clearly, that the Christian idea of
               <lb facs="#facs_71_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>equality and the Stoic in both cases was not the same. It was not Christianity but Stoicism which,
